title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 21 2022
description:
Hilarious, Herculean, Trump parody statement on Biden's covid diagnosis. C&B steak dinner bet gets serious: Feds consider charging Hunter Biden with multiple crimes, including gun-related crime. The woke left comes after Dave Chappelle again. Joining Clay and Buck for a lively discussion about the January 6th political prisoners, Nick Searcy, producer, director, and international film and TV star with a new movie, "Capitol Punishment," talks about the Jan 6th show trial.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
